text: The Sambaa K'e First Nation is a Dene First Nations band government in the Northwest Territories. The band is headquartered in the community of Sambaa K'e, formerly Trout Lake. The Sambaa K'e First Nation is a member of the Dehcho First Nations. ==References== Category:First Nations in the Northwest Territories Category:Dene governments
title: Sambaa K'e First Nation
